import React from "react"
import Input from "./Input"

function Login() {
    return (
        <form className="form">
        <Input
        type="text"
        placeholder="username"
        />
        <Input
        type="password"
        placeholder="password"
        />
        <button type="submit">Login</button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default Login
